Token.Abstract: Callback object to be used to proceed in user registration process when registration credentials for the user in question have been obtained.
Proceed with user registration by providing a valid signature and sequence which will be used in signing the registration request.

Parameter.Name: signature
Parameter.Abstract: Signature which have been obtained for a specific user and sequence.

Parameter.Name: sequence
Parameter.Abstract: Sequence identifier for the correspoding signature

Token.Abstract: If the application fails to provide a signature and sequence, it must notify the Sinch client via this method.

Parameter.Name: error
Parameter.Abstract: Error that prevented obtaining a registration sequence and signature.
